    DockingFramesPreference

    PreferenceTreePanel
    A panel that shows a JTree and a PreferenceTable.

Package bibliothek.extension.gui.dock Description

Extensions to the Core framework, including the BubbleTheme, EclipseTheme and the preference mechanism. These extensions are not necessary to run an application, but they are conveniently stored directly within the library.
